  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Decent classrooms for 200pupils at Grapevine Sch.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Grapevine Hope Centre is a community based school. The school operate from shags- classrooms made of EARTHEN FLOORS and OLD IRON SHEETS. During the dry season, it is very dusty. Children are prone to jigger infestation. During the rain season, the classrooms are muddy, slippery &amp; in general a deplorable state. Furthermore, more often, children are cut especially the young ones as they play with the iron sheets. Education is the only way out of poverty. We need to give these children hope.</narrative>
  </description>
